Full Description: Rachel's Vineyard is a healing ministry for those who have suffered the trauma of abortion. They renew, rebuild, and redeem hearts broken by abortion. Weekend retreats offer you a supportive, confidential, and non-judgmental environment where women and men can express, release, and reconcile painful post-abortive emotions to begin the process of restoration, renewal, and healing. They offer hope and healing to thousands of post-abortive men and women.
